{"tid":1995332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲少女留遺書天恒邨墮樓　當場命殞","createTime":"2020-04-30T07:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T23:54:39.000Z","uid":66507,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"17a898bc3da00c49a9d3199536ca6fa9d1348a14","tid":1995332,"uid":66507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"今日（30日）凌晨接近1時，一名17歲少女被發現在天水圍天恒邨恒健樓墮樓，她昏迷倒臥大廈對開。救護員到場證實女事主當場死亡，並用白布遮蓋遺體，警員於現場檢獲遺書，初步調查相信事主在上址一單位墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待剖屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626"},{"pid":"124911a902631202727dcddfa08e9e54452e32bc","tid":1995332,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"17歲小妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e729fe1816740fc86c35a2dda3ee3592247149","tid":1995332,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"遺書內容呢？"},{"pid":"d2b9996aef137f5a3e101b78e1f582391c329f47","tid":1995332,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"又自殺"},{"pid":"bced6c3ca4156d289828efd44b2982f573dda2de","tid":1995332,"uid":66507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4ae84bb17ce9488a188496b561dc798d10ed3f","tid":1995332,"uid":75655,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:45:52.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7677e58a48a1ddfaf9e4e5e9929215a268ec5581","tid":1995332,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cited